      "path": "/books/nahj-al-balagha:1:78:2",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/1/78/2",
      "text": [
        "اللَّهُمَّ اغْفِرْ لِي مَا أَنْتَ أَعْلَمُ بِهِ مِنِّي، فَإِنْ عُدْتُ فَعُدْ لي بِالْمَغْفِرَةِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
          "O my Allāh! Forgive me what Thou knowest about me more than I do. If I return (to the sins) Thou return to forgiveness."
        ]
      }
    }
  },
